channel.title: Starting to play RuneScape again
channel.description:
Alright, it's summer and it's time to start playing RuneScape again. During sometime in the winter, I was scammed out of 57M, ruining my chances of me wanting to play again, until now.
Before I buy Membership again, I'd like to gain enough money for a whip and full rune which will get me started on my way to playing and gaining money again. I'd like to know what I can do to make money. I have around 75WC. My combat skills are: Attack - 70 Strength - 70 and Defence - 65.
Note that I am FTP for now. Any tips will be taken into consideration. Thanks guis.
EDIT: Buying Mils may be an option but I only have around 6$CAD so if you know someone personally/on a site that is EXTREMELY TRUSTED, also let me know.
